      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5295 - It is narrated by Uthman ibn Isa from Sama'ah from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) who said:\nI asked Imam (as) about the fingers - whether some of them have more value over others in terms of blood money (diyyah).\nImam (as) replied: \"They are all equal in blood money (diyyah).\""
        ]
